<H2>
<FONT SIZE="-1">
org.springframework.test.context</FONT>
<BR>
Interface ContextLoader</H2>
<DL>
<DT><B>All Known Implementing Classes:</B> <DD><A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/AbstractContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support">AbstractContextLoader</A>, <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/AbstractGenericContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support">AbstractGenericContextLoader</A>, <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/GenericPropertiesContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support">GenericPropertiesContextLoader</A>, <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/GenericXmlContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support">GenericXmlContextLoader</A></DD>
</DL>
<HR>
<DL>
<DT><PRE>public interface <B>ContextLoader</B></DL>
</PRE>

<P>
Strategy interface for loading an
 <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/context/ApplicationContext.html" title="interface in org.springframework.context"><CODE>application context</CODE></A>.

 <p>Clients of a ContextLoader should call
 <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/ContextLoader.html#processLocations(java.lang.Class, java.lang.String...)"><CODE>processLocations()</CODE></A> prior to
 calling <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/ContextLoader.html#loadContext(java.lang.String...)"><CODE>loadContext()</CODE></A> in case the
 ContextLoader provides custom support for modifying or generating locations.
 The results of <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/ContextLoader.html#processLocations(java.lang.Class, java.lang.String...)"><CODE>processLocations()</CODE></A>
 should then be supplied to <A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/ContextLoader.html#loadContext(java.lang.String...)"><CODE>loadContext()</CODE></A>.

 <p>Concrete implementations must provide a <code>public</code> no-args
 constructor.

 <p>Spring provides the following out-of-the-box implementations:
 <ul>
 <li><A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/GenericXmlContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support"><CODE>GenericXmlContextLoader</CODE></A></li>
 <li><A HREF="../../../../org/springframework/test/context/support/GenericPropertiesContextLoader.html" title="class in org.springframework.test.context.support"><CODE>GenericPropertiesContextLoader</CODE></A></li>
 </ul>
<P>

